{"tid":1827608,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(Amazon Prime) BBC英劇 Fleabag邋遢鬼 討論區","createTime":"2020-01-17T05:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:50:19.000Z","uid":240448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"421e379cca9d73d14bbf3fef3b9319b14baafb7a","tid":1827608,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgyUw3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgyUw3U.jpg&h=83da4a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04UP5oX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04UP5oX.jpg&h=6e0d6897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n短短兩季共十二集的《Fleabag》，卻是無與倫比的閃亮，很久沒見過幾乎所有英國媒體都瞓身讚這套劇集，第一季她的尖酸自嘲self-loathing，極mean但好好笑，底子非常dark，劇中好友之死帶來的陰影籠罩全季；第二季來個180度轉身，帶來溫暖、希望和愛，打這幾個字有點肉麻，但這是事實，而且肉麻得來仍然好笑，你估易呀！跟Ricky Gervais 新作《After Life》一樣，人生縱有許多不如意，甚或無法逆轉的慘事，但身邊還有很多人、很多事，值得珍惜。<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://medium.com/@tvdramaqueen/我會掛念妳-fleabag-c73298130ca8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40tvdramaqueen%2F%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E6%8E%9B%E5%BF%B5%E5%A6%B3-fleabag-c73298130ca8&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyhIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=3e1f8e63\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@tvdramaqueen/我會掛念妳-fleabag-c73298130ca8</a><br />\n<br />\n從這十二集中，處處可見她的失敗，劇終時仍然沒有好轉，可是我仍然認為它很圓滿。第一季的《倫敦生活》，每一幀都散發着「喪」的氣息，隔着螢幕都能感受到空氣中散發着潮濕的黴味，令人窒息。黑色幽默更讓人笑着笑着便哭了出來。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/321918/倫敦生活-女主角竟然係-嗜血嬌娃-編劇-兩劇齊播一樣高收\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F321918%2F%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%9F%E7%84%B6%E4%BF%82-%E5%97%9C%E8%A1%80%E5%AC%8C%E5%A8%83-%E7%B7%A8%E5%8A%87-%E5%85%A9%E5%8A%87%E9%BD%8A%E6%92%AD%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3%E9%AB%98%E6%94%B6&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyhIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=1f9aaf43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/321918/倫敦生活-女主角竟然係-嗜血嬌娃-編劇-兩劇齊播一樣高收</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itYmb4G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitYmb4G.png&h=cfe0ef78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KC1SiKH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKC1SiKH.png&h=c37827c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aae515a593178216a8c9b8c78726c376eb245781","tid":1827608,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZMOBzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZMOBzM.jpg&h=7fc9664d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pc6u5s7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPc6u5s7.jpg&h=7d114888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjNqDN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjNqDN9.jpg&h=1532e2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LD6ZJeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLD6ZJeT.jpg&h=6cc391c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe1815e84ce2c67cc16ec87cf9e2af0ee22140fc","tid":1827608,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"樓主岩岩睇左2集 覺得好正<br />\n我知我遲左追 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲係咪都追哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"01123705251798876cde1e41906bf5699ac22f63","tid":1827608,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0NFS3go.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0NFS3go.jpg&h=350ca303&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55a9b3ad181187e728b128b6894765bbd20e5768","tid":1827608,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0